      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/claude-for-business" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Claude for business (hub) →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/services/implementation" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Treetop Implementation →</a></li>
      
    </ul>
